/>
</div> </div>
<figcaption id="mntl-figure-caption_1-0" class="comp mntl-figure-caption figure-article-caption">
<span class="figure-article-caption-owner"><p>Â <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Mojtaba_Salimi" title="User:Mojtaba Salimi" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="externalLink" data-ordinal="1">Mojtaba Salimi</a></p></span>
</figcaption>
</figure>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_2-0-2" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
<p>Moderate Reformist Hassan Rouhani won re-election in the 2017 presidential elections by a very wide margin when he defeated his conservative challenger, Ebrahim Raisi. His landslide victory was seen as a mandate to &#34;<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/20/world/middleeast/iran-election-hassan-rouhani.html" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="externalLink" data-ordinal="1">continue his quest</a> to expand personal freedoms and open Iranâ€™s ailing economy to global investors.&#34; The victory is a strong signal that everyday Iranian citizens want to engage with the outside world in spite of the restrictions placed on them by their supreme leader.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="billboard1-sticky_1-0" class="comp scads-to-load right-rail__item billboard1-sticky billboard-sticky" data-height="1050">
<div class="spacer">
<div id="billboard1_1-0" class="comp billboard1 mntl-gpt-adunit gpt billboard ">
<div id="billboard" class="wrapper"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="list-sc-item_1-0-1" class="comp mntl-sc-list-item list-sc-item mntl-block">
<div id="list-marker_1-0-1" class="comp list-marker list-marker--numbers">
<div class="content-list-number">
<div class="item-number">02</div>
<div class="total">of 03</div>
</div>
</div>
<a class="heading-toc" id="whos-who-in-irans-realm-of-power"></a> <h2 id="mntl-sc-block_2-0-3" class="comp mntl-sc-list-item-title mntl-sc-block reference-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text"> Who&#39;s Who in Iran&#39;s Realm of Power </span> </h2>
<figure id="mntl-sc-block_2-0-4" class="comp mntl-sc-block reference-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image figure-landscape figure-high-res">
<div class="figure-media">
<div class="img-placeholder" style="padding-bottom:70.7%; height:0; background-color:#c7c7c7;">
<img
