<a class="heading-toc" id="iranian-opposition"></a> <h2 id="mntl-sc-block_2-0-6" class="comp mntl-sc-list-item-title mntl-sc-block reference-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text"> Iranian Opposition </span> </h2>
<figure id="mntl-sc-block_2-0-7" class="comp mntl-sc-block reference-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image figure-landscape figure-high-res">
<div class="figure-media">
<div class="img-placeholder" style="padding-bottom:66.5%; height:0; background-color:#c7c7c7;">
<img
data-srcset="https://www.thoughtco.com/thmb/e6dAlj99bFvyjjaYwqM1fiFj5dQ=/300x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/rajavi_83814606-56aa1e225f9b58b7d000ee60.jpg 300w, https://www.thoughtco.com/thmb/jVMp4PfxocNvV1zAp-msAEVh0Eg=/975x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/rajavi_83814606-56aa1e225f9b58b7d000ee60.jpg 975w, https://www.thoughtco.com/thmb/fZElumOSabUgCYVJWdKufgB3jQ0=/1650x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/rajavi_83814606-56aa1e225f9b58b7d000ee60.jpg 1650w, https://www.thoughtco.com/thmb/JE3KvZEtyFyAp8RXnzZShiTci5E=/3000x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/rajavi_83814606-56aa1e225f9b58b7d000ee60.jpg 3000w"
