<a id="mntl-card_1-0" class="comp is-inverted-small mntl-card card" data-doc-id="2353040" data-tax-levels href="https://www.thoughtco.com/current-situation-in-the-middle-east-2353040" data-cta="Read Now â–¸" data-ordinal="1">
