<div class="card__title"><span>Current Situation in the Middle East</span></div>
</div>
</a>
</li>
<li id="masonry-list__item_1-0-1" class="comp masonry-list__item mntl-block">
<a id="mntl-card_1-0-1" class="comp is-inverted-small mntl-card card" data-doc-id="4846003" data-tax-levels href="https://www.thoughtco.com/hezbollah-history-organization-and-ideology-4846003" data-cta="Read Now â–¸" data-ordinal="2">
<div class="card__media" >
<img
data-src="https://www.thoughtco.com/thmb/PUyZcrgevxQIOoZ1zHS-2RO4UL4=/400x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/GettyImages-71973645-6f094d22871a4f7f8e60c7ae5b99ab11.jpg"
